name: dYdX
public_notice: Effective June 13, 2025, the dYdX Chain has ceased support for the wethDYDX Smart Contract (“the Bridge”). As a result, ethDYDX can no longer be converted to DYDX, and any tokens sent to the Bridge will be locked and not credited on the dYdX Chain. For more information, please read: this migration guide and Proposal #254.
